name: Boss Intermediate Extensions
author: CJ5Boss
description: Expands production trees of the Intermediate employyes Developer, Designer, Lead Developer, and SysAdmin, with additional recipe edits for related recipes. Please see github.com/CJ5-Z/BossIntermediateExtensions for all related mod info.
